        "description": "<p>Light-XML Sitemap dynamically creates dynamic XML Sitemap that comply with Google Sitemap protocol. Upon activate, you will be able to select within few clicks which content must be include or exclude from the sitemap.<\/p>\n<h3>License<\/h3>\n<p>Good news, this plugin is free for everyone! Since it&#8217;s released under the GPL, you can use it free of charge on your personal or commercial site.<\/p>\n",
